DC token usage\n58: - Environment protection rules\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ## Performance Optimization\n63: \n64: - Caching strategies\n65: - Parallel job execution\n66: - Skipping redundant runs\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## Monitoring & Observability\n71: \n72: - Workflow run metrics\n73: - Failure alerting\n74: - Duration tracking\n75: \n76: (End of file)\n\n(End of file - total 76 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n## Overview\n\n[TODO: High-level design overview]\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Workflow Directory Structure\n\n```\n.github/\n└── workflows/\n    ├── ci/\n    │   ├── build.yml\n    │   ├── test.yml\n    │   ├── lint.yml\n    │   └── security.yml\n    ├── cd/\n    │   ├── deploy-staging.yml","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-034/design.md","time":{"start":1775877295241,"end":1775877295256}}}}
