{"type":"text","timestamp":1775877325238,"sessionID":"ses_28577a81dffeT1hpF7yR7kDj6W","part":{"id":"prt_d7a896a480017rxgG22qvqLD2R","messageID":"msg_d7a894086001lhBOEmXPLSjnKI","sessionID":"ses_28577a81dffeT1hpF7yR7kDj6W","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-034 documentation and the 12 workflow files in `.github/workflows/`:\n\n## Completed\n\nAll 12 workflows are implemented:\n\n| # | Workflow File | Purpose |\n|---|---------------|---------|\n| 1 | `main.yml` | Docker build on PR |\n| 2 | `lint.yml` | Go lint (golangci-lint) |\n| 3 | `python-lint.yml` | Python lint with Ruff |\n| 4 | `codespell.yml` | Spelling checks |\n| 5 | `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright header validation |\n| 6 | `codegen-check.yml` | Code generation drift detection |\n| 7 | `test-coverage.yml` | Go test coverage with Codecov |\n| 8 | `e2e.yml` | End-to-end tests on Kind |\n| 9 | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK unit tests |\n| 10 | `build-push-release.yml` | Release image publishing to GHCR |\n| 11 | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify plugin packaging & PR |\n| 12 | `workflows-approve.yml` | First-time contributor approval automation |\n\n## Deferred\n\n**None explicitly documented as deferred.** All 12 workflows specified in the delta-spec are present.\n\nHowever, the design document (`changes/AR-034/design.md:11-27`) planned a subdirectory structure (`ci/`, `cd/`, `utils/`) which was not implemented — workflows are flat in `.github/workflows/`. The tasks.md file has empty TODO placeholders rather than detailed task tracking.","time":{"start":1775877325236,"end":1775877325236}}}
